Founder, Director of LabCentral and Chairman of Boston Heart Diagnostics. 25+ years life sciences venture capital.



Judith Li
Director
Partner with Lilly Asia Ventures. Formerly McKinsey’s healthcare practice. MBA Harvard Business School. BA Neurobiology from Harvard.











